enhanced_by.reason: The append method is used to append AstNode objects, which is a prerequisite for the prefix method to function correctly.
The withParenthesize method configures the parenthesization behavior, which can affect the output of the prefix method.
Both prefix and infix methods handle operator calls and can be used to construct similar assertions for testing operator handling.
The appendLiteral method appends literal values, which can be compared to the output of the prefix method for testing literal handling.
